5→                    <tbody>\n   696→                    </tbody>\n   697→                </table>\n   698→\n   699→            </div>\n   700→        </div>\n   701→    </div>\n   702→</section>\n   703→<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"team\"></span>\n   704→<section class=\"team\">\n   705→    <div class=\"container padding-2x\">\n   706→        <div class=\"row text-wrap\">\n   707→            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n   708→                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Meet Our Team</h3>\n   709→                <hr>\n   710→                <p class=\"text-center\">Many people contribute to Quarkus, but these 5 Red Hatters were the ones who started the project\n   711→                </p>\n   712→            </div>\n   713→        </div>\n   714→        <div class=\"row team-boxes\">\n   715→            <div class=\"col-md-2 col-md-offset-1\">\n   716→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"400ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   717→                    <img src=\"images/headshots/emmanuel-bernard.jpg\" alt=\"Emmanuel Bernard\" />\n   718→                    <h6>Emmanuel Bernard</h6>\n   719→                    <p>Co-Founder / Co-Lead</p>\n   720→                </div>\n   721→            </div>\n   722→            <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n   723→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"800ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   724→                    <img src=\"images/headshots/jason-greene.jpg\" alt=\"Jason Greene\" />\n   725→                    <h6>Jason Greene</h6>\n   726→                    <p>Co-Founder / Co-Lead</p>\n   727→                </div>\n   728→            </div>\n   729→            <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n   730→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1.2s\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   731→                    <img src=\"images/headshots/ken_avatar_2019.png\" alt=\"Ken Finnigan\" />\n   732→                    <h6>Ken Finnigan</h6>\n   733→                    <p>Pre-Quarkus Co-Founder</p>\n   734→                </div>\n   735→            </div>\n   736→            <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n   737→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1.6s\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   738→                    <img src=\"images/headshots/max-andersen.jpg\" alt=\"Max Andersen\" />\n   739→                    <h6>Max Andersen</h6>\n   740→                    <p>Devex Lead</p>\n   741→                </div>\n   742→            </div>\n   743→            <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n   744→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1.6s\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   745→                    <img src=\"images/headshots/clement_escoffier.jpeg\" alt=\"Clement Escoffier\" />\n   746→                    <h6>Clement Escoffier</h6>\n   747→                    <p>Reactive Lead</p>\n   748→                </div>\n   749→            </div>\n   750→        </div>\n   751→    </div>\n   752→</section>\n   753→<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"testimonials\"></span>\n   754→<section class=\"testimonials\">\n   755→    <div id=\"carousel-testimonials\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-bs-ride=\"carousel\">\n   756→        <div class=\"container-fluid padding-2x\">\n   757→            <!-- Wrapper for slides -->\n   758→            <div class=\"row\">\n   759→                <div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n   760→                    <h3 class=\"text-center\">Twitter</h3>\n   761→                    <hr>\n   762→                </div>\n   763→            </div>\n   764→            <div class=\"row\">\n   765→                <div class=\"col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3\">\n   766→                    <div class=\"carousel-inner\">\n   767→                        <div class=\"carousel-item active\">\n   768→                            <div class=\"carousel-content\">\n   769→                                <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet tw-align-center \"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I really like <a href=\"https://twitter.com/QuarkusIO?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@QuarkusIO</a>&#39;s extension system. The deployment time (build time) hook allows for a lot of interesting uses I haven&#39;t thought of yet 🚀</p>&mdash; Knut Wannheden (@knutwannheden) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/knutwannheden/status/1276588974849634304?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 26, 2020</a></blockquote> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n   770→                            </div>\n   771→                        </div>\n   772→                        <div class=\"carousel-item\">\n   773→                            <div class=\"carousel-content\">\n   774→                                <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet tw-align-center \"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">“One of the real benefits of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Java?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Java</a> is that it does have a huge <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ecosystem?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ecosystem</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/libraries?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#libraries</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/utilities?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#utilities</a> for doing practically everything.&quot; Therefore, consider using the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Quarkus?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Quarkus</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/framework?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#framework</a> for your next <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/microservice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#microservice</a> project. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/QuarkusIO?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@QuarkusIO</a><a href=\"https://t.co/Z6JNMFSxab\">https://t.co/Z6JNMFSxab</a></p>&mdash; Felix Seifert (@flx_seifert) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/flx_seifert/status/1274708071630045185?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 21, 2020</a></blockquote> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n   775→                            </div>\n   776→                        </div>\n   777→                        <div class=\"carousel-item\">\n   778→                            <div class=\"carousel-content\">\n   779→                                <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet tw-align-center \"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">⚡️New: Running a native image on AWS <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Lambda?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Lambda</a> through <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Quarkus?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Quarkus</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GraalVM?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#GraalVM</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sascha242?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@sascha242</a> and me examine the benefits you can get and describe the build steps required for your <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Java?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Java</a> app. <a href=\"https://t.co/yRSSEvOSuz\">https://t.co/yRSSEvOSuz</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/6H7OOi3geF\">pic.twitter.com/6H7OOi3geF</a></p>&mdash; Steffen Grunwald (@steffeng) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/steffeng/status/1273485530030903298?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 18, 2020</a></blockquote> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n   780→                            </div>\n   781→                        </div>\n   782→                        <!-- Indicators -->\n   783→                        <div class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n   784→                            <button type=\"button\" data-bs-target=\"#carousel-testimonials\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\" aria-current=\"true\" aria-label=\"Slide 1\"></button>\n   785→                            <button type=\"button\" data-bs-target=\"#carousel-testimonials\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\" aria-label=\"Slide 2\"></button>\n   786→                            <button type=\"button\" data-bs-target=\"#carousel-testimonials\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" aria-label=\"Slide 3\"></button>\n   787→                        </div>\n   788→                    </div>\n   789→                </div>\n   790→            </div>\n   791→        </div>\n   792→    </div>\n   793→</section>\n   794→<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"gallery\"></span>\n   795→<section class=\"gallery\">\n   796→    <div class=\"container padding-2x\">\n   797→        <div class=\"row text-wrap\">\n   798→            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n   799→                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Gallery</h3>\n   800→                <hr>\n   801→                <p class=\"text-center\">Pictures of café like things that lend an air of verisimillitude to our demo.</p>\n   802→            </div>\n   803→        </div>\n   804→        <div class=\"row gallery-images justify-content-center\">\n   805→            <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n   806→                <div class=\"row\">\n   807→                    <div class=\"col-md-4 image wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"100ms\" >\n   808→                        <a href=\"images/gallery1.png\" data-bs-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"lava-gallery\">\n   809→                            <img src=\"images/gallery1.png\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"gallery1\">\n   810→                        </a>\n   811→                    </div>\n   812→                    <div class=\"col-md-4 image wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"200ms\" >\n   813→                        <a href=\"images/gallery2.png\" data-bs-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"lava-gallery\">\n   814→                            <img src=\"images/gallery2.png\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"gallery2\">\n   815→                        </a>\n   816→                    </div>\n   817→                    <div class=\"col-md-4 image wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"300ms\" >\n   818→                        <a href=\"images/gallery3.png\" data-bs-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"lava-gallery\">\n   819→                            <img src=\"images/gallery3.png\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=